				<div id="left-sbm-top">
					<h1>Trade and Competitiveness</h1>  
															        
					<div id="node-161" class="node node-issue_area">



  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <img  class="imagefield imagefield-field_image" width="200" height="120" alt="" src="../files/chinainfo/chinafaqs-trade.png?1255708640" />        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p>The nexus of trade, competitiveness, and climate change is part of the debate surrounding the U.S.-China relationship.  How will climate policy affect U.S. trade and competitiveness with China, and &#8211; on the flip side &#8211; how are trade policies affecting energy and emissions?</p>

<p><a href="../blog-posts/trade-cases-imports-clean-energy-products-china">Click here</a> for a collection of resources and statements from official sources, media, and concerned groups regarding U.S.-China clean energy trade issues.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block">
    <div class="meta">
        </div>

      </div>

</div>
